title: Bass 2 Billfish: Stickmarsh Fishing and Paddleboard Tarpon
text:
Updated: 5:17 p.m. Monday, Oct. 5, 2015 | Posted: 4:36 p.m. Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015 Bass 2 Billfish: Stickmarsh Fishing and Paddleboard Tarpon In Partnership with VisitFlorida.com 
Bass 2 Billfish host Peter Miller takes his lifelong friends Matt Doane and Peter Simonelli on a unique fishing adventure for largemouth bass on Stickmarsh/Farm #13 with the help of Capt. Dean Herdman . After slaying the bass, they took an unforgettable paddleboard trip in search of tarpon and snook with Cory Redwine, the guide and owner of All Water Adventures .
